## What Is the Minimum Deposit at Exness?

Exness is known for its ultra-low deposit barrier. Traders can start with as little as:

* **\$1 USD** (or equivalent in local currency)
* **KES 150** in Kenya
* **ZAR 19** in South Africa
* **₦400** in Nigeria

> 💡 Actual minimums may vary slightly depending on your **payment method** or **local currency**.

---

## Minimum Deposit by Account Type

| **Account Type** | **Minimum Deposit** | **Ideal For**              |
| ---------------- | ------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Standard         | \$1                 | Beginners                  |
| Standard Cent    | \$1                 | Micro-lot, low-risk trades |
| Raw Spread       | \$100               | Advanced traders           |
| Zero             | \$100               | Scalpers, EA users         |
| Pro              | \$100               | Experienced professionals  |

> ✅ **Standard and Cent accounts** are best if you want to start small.

