## Deposit Currencies and Local Equivalents

Exness supports deposits in over 80 currencies. Here are some popular options:

* USD, EUR, GBP
* ZAR (South African Rand)
* KES (Kenyan Shilling)
* NGN (Nigerian Naira)
* THB, IDR, VND

This helps you avoid conversion fees and deposit in your native currency.

