## Payment Methods Accepted

Exness offers a wide range of global and local payment options:

* 💳 Credit/Debit Cards (Visa, Mastercard)
* 🏦 Bank Transfers
* 📱 Mobile Payments (e.g. M-Pesa, Airtel)
* 💼 E-wallets: Skrill, Neteller, Perfect Money
* 🪙 Crypto: BTC, USDT, ETH

> 🔁 Most methods support **instant** and **fee-free** transactions.

