## Pros & Cons of Low Deposit Trading

**Pros:**

* ✅ Start trading with almost no capital
* ✅ Ideal for learning without high risk
* ✅ Instant access to live markets

**Cons:**

* ❌ Limited margin & leverage with micro-capital
* ❌ Less room for diversification

